    "description": "If you're a passionate Sales Manager with drive and ambition, Oberoi Realty Global Group in Jodhpur is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Oberoi Realty Global Group:\nOberoi Realty Global Group is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in Lease Administration\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jodhpur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Oberoi Realty Global Group!",
